# Per-task corpus is single-sourced from harbor_adapters/contextbench/vendor/files/
# and regenerated via `python -m harbor_adapters.contextbench.main --populate <dir>`.
*/environment/files/

# The verifier files below are byte-identical across every task, so they are
# single-sourced (harbor_adapters/contextbench/templates/ + vendor/rubric.txt)
# and regenerated by the same `--populate` step. Only tests/case.json (the
# per-task question + ground truth) is committed.
*/tests/test.sh
*/tests/judge.py
*/tests/rubric.txt
